    <sec id="sec-molecules-10-01119" sec-type="conclusions">
      <title>Conclusions</title>
      <p>Seventeen target compounds were prepared and tested for their herbicidal activities. A new facile synthetic route was developed with methyl <italic>N</italic>-substituted iminomonoacetate as starting material. The collective results show that 2-phenyl-tetrahydro-2<italic>H</italic>-pyrido[1,2-a]pyrazine-1,3(4<italic>H</italic>,6<italic>H</italic>)-dione provided better herbicidal activity.</p>
    </sec>
